		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#b15a9c" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#b15a9c">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1658" y="48" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="218" height="34" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.5019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="right" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" color="#ffffff">元素能量：NA</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#f57ede" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔原地掷击地面，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">30%</span><span>伤害，并召唤4枚月影，依次朝玩家发射光束，均造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>伤害。<br/>「血雾隐匿」下不出现月影；瘫痪恢复后连续施放3次，第三次召唤月影。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔从远处伏爪冲击而来，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="438" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">近距离攻击闲逛的雷利尔时，受击3次后触发格挡，立即造成<span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">战斗进行一段时间后，雷利尔扬起血雾，进入「血雾隐匿」状态，交替施放技能；期间全队流血：每2s损失当前<span color="#ffbfbf">1.5%生命值</span><span>，不致死。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔进行戳、挑、猛戳至多3段的普通攻击，依次造成<span color="#b8b8b8">15%,20%,20%</span><span>伤害，可后接技能「将那黑日谖忘」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="1151" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔立即进行数圈的旋转攻击，持续造成<span color="#b8b8b8">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1375" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于雷利尔后侧时，雷利尔扔出5枚暗刻之刺，每枚造成<span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>伤害，并立即后接技能「斩阵狂殄八方」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1599" width="441" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">战斗进行一段时间后，雷利尔起飞至空中蓄力，展开结界，在场地内持续随机生成虚棘和<span textDecoration="underline">月矩粒</span><span>，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">15%</span><span>伤害；25s后灾劫降下，</span><span color="#ffbfbf">秒杀</span><span>不处于</span><span textDecoration="underline">护罩</span><span>下的角色，对处于护罩下的角色造成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">20%生命值</span><span>的伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔闲逛时，其周围会出现2枚月影，对玩家发射黑矢，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="431" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔突然跃来，朝地猛击，并引发爆裂，依次造成<span color="#b8b8b8">30%,40%</span><span>伤害，为绝大部分技能的后接技。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔进行转、转圈、猛戳至多3段的普通攻击，依次造成<span color="#b8b8b8">20%,25%x2,25%</span><span>伤害，可后接技能「斩阵狂殄八方」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="1375" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔立即进行数圈的旋转攻击，持续造成<span color="#b8b8b8">30%</span><span>伤害，旋转结束后立即后接技能「斩阵狂殄八方」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1599" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔划出一道裂缝，飞出4枚虚星，每枚造成<span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>伤害，并立即朝玩家处回斩，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷利尔飞速地进行至多6段的普通攻击，依次造成<span color="#b8b8b8">5%,20%,25%,5%,5%,25%</span><span>伤害，若目标距离较远，则第三段普攻后闪现至目标侧位继续攻击或后接技能。<br/>「血雾隐匿」下只施放后三段攻击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/猎月人%B7雷利尔.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1392" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
